      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，起源下面放\"悠久历史\"（Long history），然后普及化（Popularisation）要单独列出来，归功于英国的那位著名心理学作者Tony Buzan。另外，悠久历史旁边我想加个零售库存的图标。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Long history",
        "Popularisation",
        "British popular psychology author Tony Buzan",
